  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is (1) to establish the feasibility, yield, and clinical impact of
      a &quot;Test &amp; Treat TB&quot; strategy on a mobile HIV screening unit in South Africa and (2) to assess
      the cost and cost-effectiveness of this mobile, integrated HIV/TB screening strategy for
      maximizing linkage to TB care and treatment completion.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
